1665702843526.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qfx1665702843526.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qfx1665702843526.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qfx1665702843526\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qfx1665702843526___appltitle_252812\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return or set the window title bar text of a Uniface Windows application.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__topic_d80441e1_d80442e1_d80443e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__p_d80444e1_d80445e1_d80446e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$appltitle</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__p_d80447e1_d80448e1_d80449e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$appltitle</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ApplicationTitle</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__topic_d52947e1_d52948e1_d52949e1_d52950e1_d52951e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d588767e77\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__p_d80453e1_d80454e1_d80455e1\">Title of the application window.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__topic_d52952e1_d52953e1_d52954e1_d52955e1_d52956e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d588767e86\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__d6512e20\">Use only in Application Shell and Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__topic_d52957e1_d52958e1_d52959e1_d52960e1_d52961e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d588767e95\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfx1665702843526__p_d80465e1_d80466e1_d80467e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$appltitle</span> function has effect only when the application is using a GUI driver. Changing <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$appltitle</span> overrides the value defined in the GUI-specific settings.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531245\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531245\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$appltitle Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return or set the window title bar text of a Uniface Windows application. $appltitle $appltitle = ApplicationTitle Return Values Title of the application window. Use Use only in Application Shell and Form components. Description The $appltitle function has effect only when the application is using a GUI driver. Changing $appltitle overrides the value defined in the GUI-specific settings. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}